      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For example, you can extend the on-premises network and Active Domain Directory to the cloud via <ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/documentation/articles/virtual-networks-overview/\"&gt;</ph>Azure Network Services<ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph>.",
      "pos": [
        9698,
