      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In addition, you can store on-premises data files in Azure Storage using the <ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;a href=\"http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/dn385720.aspx\"&gt;</ph>SQL Server Data Files in Azure feature<ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph>.",
