    {
      "content": "With <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Azure SQL Database<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, Microsoft administers the physical hardware such as hard drives, servers, and storage; automatically replicates all data to provide high availability; configures and upgrades the database software; manages load balancing; and does transparent failover if there is a server failure.",
